data.description:
OPEN HOUSE SATURDAY 10-4pm! Discover a stunning 3-bed, 2-bath home just minutes from Maxwell Air Force Base. The large entrance opens to a spacious living
room with a gas log fireplace. The primary suite features a large bathroom with a jacuzzi tub, walk-in shower, and closet. The kitchen offers ample counter space and
storage. A 4-season sunroom leads to a covered patio and a manicured backyard. An extra-large building awaits your creative use—whether a studio, storage, or
potential living space. Unwind in your private backyard with a glass of wine or cup of hot chocolate. This property seamlessly combines comfort and elegance, making it
a desirable and welcoming home.
